data.description: Come see this cute, updated St. Joseph schools ranch home in a fabulous neighborhood close to shopping, highway access, schools & parks.  Open flow from kitchen to dining to living. Easy to maintain brick exterior.  Home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 3 season room.  Fenced backyard, partially finished basement with home office.  Wood burning fireplace. Patio for entertaining.  Driveway is 2 cars wide for extra parking.  This one won't last long!
